290
00:21:37,110 --> 00:21:38,280
Shinichirou!

291
00:22:01,330 --> 00:22:03,070
Ai-chan...

292
00:22:03,730 --> 00:22:04,830
Please...

293
00:22:06,370 --> 00:22:08,260
Look at me too...

294
00:22:10,260 --> 00:22:11,470
Please...

295
00:22:13,220 --> 00:22:14,390
Shinichirou...

296
00:23:50,750 --> 00:23:53,130
Is it okay if I fall in love with you even more?

297
00:23:54,180 --> 00:23:58,810
With such a docile face, she was easily able to catch a man's heart.

298
00:23:59,780 --> 00:24:00,810
It's a game.

